Screenshot*.png
Screenshot*.jpg

# Generated OpenAPI artifacts. Authority is the Huma route source; the
# action graph rebuilds these into bazel-out via verself_openapi_specs +
# verself_oapi_go_client. No on-disk source of truth.
src/*/openapi/openapi-*.yaml
src/*/openapi/internal-openapi-*.yaml
src/*/client/client.gen.go
src/*/internalclient/client.gen.go
*.pb.go
*_grpc.pb.go
!src/substrate/vm-orchestrator/proto/v1/*.pb.go

